Here, the number N=99
Sum of the digits N: 9+9 = 18
Repeat step 2 ‘R’ times i.e. 3 tims  (9+9)+(9+9)+(9+9) = 18+18+18 =54
Add digits of 54 as we need a single digit 5+4
